Package: Rlibhv
Title: R Bindings for the 'libhv' C/C++ Network Library
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Sounkou", "Mahamane", "Toure" , "sounkoutoure@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides R bindings for the 'libhv' C/C++ networking library. 
    This package offers high-performance event-driven networking capabilities 
    including HTTP1/2 client/server, WebSocket, TCP/UDP servers, and more. 
    'libhv' is a cross-platform network library similar to'libuv'.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
SystemRequirements: pkg-config, GNU Make, curl, libcurl, openssl, zlib
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    tinytest
